projects.title: Let's Walk!
projects.about: This project involved the creation of an iOS app from scratch using the Swift programming language. If you would like to view the code, please contact me for repository access.

aboutpara: As a senior studying Information Systems, I am passionate about the intersection of technology and human desires. I have a strong interest in full stack & front-end engineering as well as design research. Through my academic coursework and extracurricular activities, I have gained technical skills in programming languages such as Java and Python, as well as experience with design principles and tools. I am eager to apply my skills and continue learning in a dynamic and challenging environment where I can collaborate with diverse teams.

resume.tagline: I'm interested in creative solutions to problems that people face everyday.
resume.description: I have diligently pursued pleasing the user in my design and development work.
